      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ORANA REX (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 3 lengths (17.42) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Better than last start and worth following up. RADIO RAMSGATE (5) is a promising dog in the frame at five of 12 starts including three wins and was in the minors again latest (17.65) over 300m at this track. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Will go close here with a clear run. ZETA PRIME (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 17.66 beating Thai Surprise. Sure to measure up. JUNK YARD JEFF (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
